 [Music] The quality and truth of our existence depend on our ability to locate and live within the heart, for it is there that God communicates with man. It is there that the new man is born renewed and raised up to commune with God today, distracted as we are by technological novelties and the cascade of information that comes with them. We buzz about our daily activities often without even recognizing that this place in the heart is where God lives and where we can find true peace.
